    "description": "Play minigolf through a variety of different courses from the designer of <strong>Sierra's 3D Ultra Minigolf</strong>.<br><br>Collect power-ups, make impossible shots, play by yourself or online against up to 20 other players. Comes with <strong>race, safari, and normal</strong> game types - more game types are being added.<br><br><strong>Wishlist it now</strong> to keep updated<br><br>Apply for Beta access on my Discord channel: <br><br>Lava Islands: Time your shots and avoid the lava. Take the safe shot or the risky high reward one.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389370/extras/1941995526c13dbb69436fffca71aa61.poster.avif?t=1700503467\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389370/extras/1941995526c13dbb69436fffca71aa61.webm?t=1700503467\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389370/extras/1941995526c13dbb69436fffca71aa61.mp4?t=1700503467\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Use some of the many Power-Ups.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389370/extras/b44e446100747a61128452589d19541a.poster.avif?t=1700503467\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389370/extras/b44e446100747a61128452589d19541a.webm?t=1700503467\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389370/extras/b44e446100747a61128452589d19541a.mp4?t=1700503467\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Hit the perfect shot to be dropped off in the cup.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"h