m<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389370/extras/a96ab85364a425d5acb7c59f05d20f04.poster.avif?t=1700503467\" width=600 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389370/extras/a96ab85364a425d5acb7c59f05d20f04.webm?t=1700503467\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389370/extras/a96ab85364a425d5acb7c59f05d20f04.mp4?t=1700503467\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Features</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Golden Hills, Lava Islands, Snowy Fields, Orc Village, and more themed 18 hole courses<br></li><li>Classic Minigolf along with Race and Safari game modes<br></li><li>Both Online Multiplayer &amp; Local Multiplayer<br></li><li>Many different ball super powers<br></li><li>Leaderboards<br></li><li>Accurate ball physics</li></ul>",
